{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_04_01",
  "title": "kana",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さ～ん\nkana、すっごい大事なお願いがあるんですけど～",
      "startTime": 2.8999999324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaさんの愛想がいい……）\n（しかも、俺に頼み事だって……？）",
      "startTime": 9.9000000278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "最近、星見プロの子達が何人も\nドラマとか映画に出演してますよね",
      "startTime": 16.8000000278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "それでですね\nkanaも演技の仕事、やってみたいな～って",
      "startTime": 22.4333333611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "ほらkana、子供の頃からモデルやってたんで\n何度かドラマにゲストで出たこともありますし",
      "startTime": 30.1666666944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。なら、そっちの人に営業かける時には\nkanaさんのことも売り込んでおきますよ",
      "startTime": 37.6333333611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとですか？　ありがとうございま～～す！！",
      "startTime": 39.8743353326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも、つまんない仕事だったら許さないからね\nkanaがモブなんてありえないし",
      "startTime": 47.5666701873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "山田さんほど、ギャラうるさくは言わないけどさ～\nでも、あんま安くても格ってもんがねぇ",
      "startTime": 53.3666701873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃は一応、映画の主役やったんでしょ\nなら月ストに勝ったkanaだって主演いけるよね？",
      "startTime": 60.5000035207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "が、頑張って営業してきます……",
      "startTime": 65.6670333664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（演技の仕事に興味が出てきたのか？　でも、そんな）\n（条件のいい仕事、すぐには入ってこないだろうなぁ）",
      "startTime": 73.2666701873,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6133.329772900012,
          "startTime": 79.3999999602
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 78.8759175103
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さ～～ん！！\n演技の仕事、決まりました～～？",
      "startTime": 83.1999791066,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そう言われても\nkanaさんに頼まれたの、まだ三日前ですよ……",
      "startTime": 87.7999811411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "ちっ、使えねぇな",
      "startTime": 91.2245880087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "あのねぇ、芸能界はスピードが命なの\nこれをやるって決めたら突っ込まないでどうすんのよ",
      "startTime": 97.5666503509,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あー……実は、話がないこともないんですけど…………\nあの直後、映画監督からぜひkanaさんにって……",
      "startTime": 106.3999836843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　なんだ、それならそうと早く言ってよ～！\nさすが星見プロの敏腕マネージャー！！",
      "startTime": 115.2999877533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "で、映画のジャンルは？　kanaの役はどんなの？",
      "startTime": 119.4301018118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "人気漫画の実写映画だそうです\n原作は確か、累計で数千万部は売れてるとか",
      "startTime": 126.3333236298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、なかなかの案件じゃん！",
      "startTime": 130.5369249065,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9475.991320700017,
          "startTime": 140.0129162272
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんに来たのは、拳法を極めた美少女の役です\n一応、監督と主演の役者さんも決まっていまして……",
      "startTime": 138.5000086071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "うーわ。この監督、最近ヒット連発してる人じゃん\n主演も若手の中ではまーまーだし",
      "startTime": 147.0333419404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "でもさぁ、そんな人からオファーあったなら\nなんで、それをすぐkanaに言わなかったわけ？",
      "startTime": 154.4333419404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "あんた、kanaのマネージャーじゃないの？\nなんのお仕事をしてらっしゃるんですか～～？",
      "startTime": 160.4333419404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ええと……実はこの仕事、断ろうと思ってまして",
      "startTime": 164.1013013244,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan018.m4a",
      "text": "………………はぁ？\nすみませ～ん、もう一度言ってもらえます～？",
      "startTime": 173.0000014865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "これから先方に断りの電話を入れるつもりだったんです\nそこに、ちょうどkanaさんが来て……",
      "startTime": 180.7666773085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan019.m4a",
      "text": "バッカじゃないの！？\nこんな美味しい仕事断るなんて、本当に業界人かよ！？",
      "startTime": 184.9000147109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan020.m4a",
      "text": "漫画原作ならある程度数字は固いし\n監督も主演も今かなり売れてるし",
      "startTime": 191.866667136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan021.m4a",
      "text": "そんな企画に一枚噛まないでどうすんのよ\n絶っ対、逃してたまるかっての！！",
      "startTime": 198.466667136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan022.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。これから電話するって言ってたよね\n今！　ここで！　映画会社に電話して",
      "startTime": 204.7000004694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "しかしですね……",
      "startTime": 208.8408397399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan023.m4a",
      "text": "さっさとやれ！！",
      "startTime": 210.2215116067,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3378.488393299989,
          "startTime": 213.6
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3845.1550599999964,
          "startTime": 214.0666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-dialtone-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4711.821726599993,
          "startTime": 214.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "は、はいっ",
      "startTime": 212.6025999906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "お世話になっております……\nはい。先日お話をいただいた、映画の件で――",
      "startTime": 218.9392202071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_01-kan024.m4a",
      "text": "お電話かわりました！　星見プロのkanaです\nご指名いただきまして、光栄に思います！",
      "startTime": 228.7806519727,
      "sfxList": [
        {
